<p><a name="Public_awareness" id="Public_awareness"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Innovation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Public awareness">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Public awareness</span></h2>
<p>Public awareness of innovation is an important part of the innovation process. This is further discussed in the emerging fields of <a href="/wiki/Innovation_journalism" title="Innovation journalism">innovation journalism</a> and <a href="/w/index.php?title=Innovation_communication&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Innovation communication (page does not exist)">innovation communication</a>.</p>
